OL,3,CNew Stadium for Cornwall plan will be
OL,4,Cfor the 'whole community'
OL,6,FPlans for a sports hub, including an
OL,7,FFA-endorsed football pitch, on the
OL,8,Fsite originally earmarked for the
OL,9,FStadium for Cornwall have taken a
OL,10,Fstep nearer to completion.
OL,12,FThe Stadium For Cornwall project was
OL,13,Fdropped in 2022 after councillors
OL,14,Fsaid there was no money in the budget
OL,15,Ffor it.
OL,17,FNow the cabinet has approved a
OL,18,Frecommendation that the new Truro
OL,19,FCommunity Sports Hub be included as
OL,20,Fpart of the 3,550-home Langarth
OL,21,FGarden Village development.
